g.text: If a lecturer is registered and logs in with her account,
her sessions remain stored for 180 days after the last visit,
otherwise they are deleted when she logs out.
Registered students can receive a bonus
as another option we have general, fond, hover and
weight-classes that apply to the sight of the cloud
it is possible to choose the language for the spelling.
